{"tid":367584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉小麗涉冒議員非法籌款","createTime":"2017-08-21T00:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T05:56:34.000Z","uid":81228,"like":21,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5b8859538f82752680fc9d51206d5cda530a7e5","tid":367584,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T00:12:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">■香港文匯報記者 齊正之、張得民</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://image.wenweipo.com/2017/08/21/a02a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.wenweipo.com%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2Fa02a.jpg&h=3a5c637f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■8月13日晚，劉小麗（左二着黑長裙者）鬼祟在荔枝角社區會堂入口外，用無標貼不透明紙盒涉嫌非法籌款。<br />\n<br />\n早前被法院依法取消立法會議員資格的「瀆誓四丑」劉小麗、梁國雄、羅冠聰、姚松炎，近期以「上訴」為名四處開街站「撲水」（籌款）。香港文匯報記者連日調查發現，這些街頭公開籌款活動都沒有按規定列在民政事務總署網頁上，有關行為涉嫌非法籌款。其中，劉小麗早前到深水埗一個社區會堂參加電影晚會時，主辦方在宣傳專頁上仍稱她是「立法會議員」，散場後更要求出席者在場外捐錢。對此，香港中小型律師行協會創會會長陳曼琪向香港文匯報表示，劉小麗有可能涉及非法籌款、藐視法庭罪及欺詐罪。<br />\n<br />\n自從7月14日被取消立法會議員資格後，劉小麗一個月來頻頻「呻窮」，四處公開籌款，聲稱要支持其「議員辦事處」運作，及支付DQ案律師費。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>義工向途人提及「議員」</strong><br />\n<br />\n8月13日下午，香港文匯報記者收到讀者舉報，指劉小麗等人在旺角太子某小學門口外涉嫌非法籌款。記者抵場後所見，校門對開路面周圍插着近十支「小麗民主教室」旗幡，劉小麗等十餘人霸佔了大半條行人路，不少街坊被迫頂着熾熱的陽光經過此處時均感不滿。<br />\n<br />\n在路旁的陰涼處，則擺放三數個透明籌款箱，但捐款者卻寥寥可數。其間，部分義工向途人募捐時亦有提及「議員」，有街坊追問是否「議員籌款打官司」？但未見現場義工澄清。至當天下午5時半左右，劉小麗似乎捱不了熱浪，就與一名男助手匆匆離開。但可能是平時坐慣的士的原因，劉小麗走到對面的始創中心門口後不停左望右望，男助手則「手指指」，兩人花了超過10分鐘，才找到100米外的太子站入口。看來，家住西九、聲稱「落地」的劉小麗，對最多市民使用的「港鐵」非常陌生。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>並無澄清「議員」稱謂</strong><br />\n<br />\n劉小麗8月13日活動的「戲肉」是當晚出席由「社區院線」及區議員在荔枝角社區會堂舉辦的電影籌款會，播放的是一套「港獨」意味甚濃的電影。在主辦此活動的「社區院線」facebook（臉書）宣傳海報上，劉小麗依然被稱為「立法會議員」。據香港文匯報記者觀察，無論是在場的劉小麗本人，還是其官網「小麗民主教室」，都未對有關稱呼作任何澄清。<br />\n<br />\n不知是什麼原因，這場電影的播放過程甚不順利，其間字幕不時出現問題，音響也欠佳，有數十名觀眾因此感到不耐煩而提早離場。在電影結束後，一名女主持邀請劉小麗及該電影的導演走到前台，進行所謂「分享」及答問環節。有台下的出席者在向劉小麗及導演提問時，直斥電影中的情節主題思想狹隘、危言聳聽，會引導年輕人作出傷害個人及社會的激進行為，同時也認為學習普通話與使用方言並無衝突，並指其子女以前沒有機會學習普通話很可惜。對此有關問題，劉小麗等人則支吾以對。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>門外持盒籲觀眾捐錢</strong><br />\n<br />\n主持人見勢不妙只好趕緊結束提問，並向在場約200名出席者表示，由於社區會堂是政府場地，因此不方便直接進行「金錢交易」，「但散場後工作人員會在門口等大家」，她並多番意有所指地說「大家明白的，要識做」。<br />\n<br />\n香港文匯報記者現場所見，在觀眾離場時，包括劉小麗在內約10人已各自拿着紙巾盒大小的籌款盒站在門口外等候，並不斷呼籲大家捐錢。不過，有數名年輕人邊離開邊竊竊私語：「海報唔係話免費嘅咩？」「算啦，佢哋咁樣企喺門口要錢，唯有焗畀啦。」<br />\n<br />\n香港文匯報記者翻查當晚「社區院線」的網上電影籌款海報，其中「費用全免」四字顯眼清晰，豈料現場有人卻走「法律罅」，要出席者「捐款」。有不滿「被捐款」的觀眾向記者表示，他本來是應友人之邀來看這場「免費電影」，「如果佢哋一早講清楚睇呢場電影要畀錢，我一定會畀；但我最唔忿有人特登『博大霧』，焗住要人捐錢。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2017/08/21/YO1708210001.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2FYO1708210001.htm&d=krH8DyAv65INnHgKr1UFuAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=dc629b4f\" target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2017/08/21/YO1708210001.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b46d4fda70b851abaa48e3ca5b62a12bddfb8170","tid":367584,"uid":11779,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T00:44:38.000Z","msg":"企到好似呠蘭街啲雞咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eab6ad2cc4ebe15f4fe265d4c2d9d422eeb025c","tid":367584,"uid":2126,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T00:50:10.000Z","msg":"文匯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3f90352fb51bb09a2934555f4dc2f82bc438a7","tid":367584,"uid":80411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T00:51:02.000Z","msg":"文匯報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62acd9efcb42f972597d982ba67a5f431d03b77","tid":367584,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T00:52:12.000Z","msg":"留番同法官講囉，登出黎把撚"},{"pid":"90a04f4845e2d4330809ac9fb285208dce577f3c","tid":367584,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T00:54:41.000Z","msg":"又倒米"},{"pid":"d7ec8a8b07894983679130132fd7c70b7eb5be1f","tid":367584,"uid":68094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T00:56:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b42cb37f21b6e7df952f616dd4fe4817eebe6b8d","tid":367584,"uid":33643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T00:58:09.000Z","msg":"香港中小型律師行協會創會會長陳曼琪<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db81d0ef18ee93022d9efa1e3d27d8ca0536fcfe","tid":367584,"uid":33643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T00:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港中小型律師行協會創會會長陳曼琪<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n陳曼琪在佔領行動時，代表潮聯小巴申請佔旺禁制令、並親自到旺角佔領區宣讀禁令內容"},{"pid":"748adeba35be926130e07f0f3a7681897d834baa","tid":367584,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:00:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港中小型律師行協會創會會長陳曼琪<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n陳曼琪在佔領行動時，代表潮聯小巴申請佔旺禁制令、並親自到旺角佔領區宣讀禁令內容</blockquote><br />\n全國人大代表將於年底舉行換屆選舉，不少政界人士亦早作部署，有消息指當中有兩名女士最為矚目，包括立法會議員梁美芬及中小型律師行協會創會會長陳曼琪，兩人均屬法律界，本來已佔優勢，加上在反佔中、反暴亂及撐高鐵一地兩檢等多場硬仗都積極表態，選情被外界看高一線。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64237b77f5c7c5bc903179ccd63334b8a7376be","tid":367584,"uid":55951,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:48:03.000Z","msg":"文匯報都當source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n李國章呢啲都唔睇文匯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e3ebe54a822d413b3545936103145473f138ae","tid":367584,"uid":102132,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:48:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ba63511224bc187801e98aa1e32c5f77329d70d","tid":367584,"uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小麗老母應該唔係好店</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小麗申報資產有2個單位，唔係好掂? <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/095106_e8458e711e447ef477d0225fb7fd6f4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F095106_e8458e711e447ef477d0225fb7fd6f4e.jpg&h=755d12eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63c82331702fb15cbfad13cd3c12e5df716500c4","tid":367584,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:54:32.000Z","msg":"神駒好波"},{"pid":"6b1d97dcfb7c6d4f2f2a08ca60f5e72e7b4defaa","tid":367584,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:01:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>神駒好波</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n生果有講，我之前睇生果，隨便google搵到"},{"pid":"9c0ce100eef0734296e3680092c94c9405733b26","tid":367584,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:17:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小麗老母應該唔係好店</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小麗申報資產有2個單位，唔係好掂? <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/095106_e8458e711e447ef477d0225fb7fd6f4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F095106_e8458e711e447ef477d0225fb7fd6f4e.jpg&h=755d12eb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n大奶奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea661703dd530783063c5950198f90c79ed6df7","tid":367584,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:20:51.000Z","msg":"支那報收皮啦"},{"pid":"cb1c1ddb06316c0b049444838c3a34466d46aa0a","tid":367584,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:35:12.000Z","msg":"文滙報涉侵犯肖像權喎&hellip;全國性法律有法不依？"},{"pid":"1c17f0dfbe369b1ac2a667b8026e8d9faef0c072","tid":367584,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:58:37.000Z","msg":"有片先講"},{"pid":"50c0dd50668d67505feee1070cb3f17f7562c45d","tid":367584,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:56:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}